node.text: @takumiitou4663 took the title at the 2021 @wearefarmers Bassmaster Elite on the St. Lawrence River. Everyone in attendance and at home witnessed Taku Time as the young angler completed a dream to win a Bassmaster Elite Series event. With an astounding 26 pounds on Day 4, Taku came from 7th place to win for the first time in his career. #bassmaster #takutime #fishing

node.title: A STAR is born, it’s Taku Time!

This allows the baits to soak in the smell and attract smallmouth to bite better. 
#Bassmaster #BassFishing #BASSElite

In today's #TackleTipTuesday video brought to you by @mercurymarine, @takumiitou4663 breaks down his keys to success at the St. Lawrence River. He heavily relies on scents and smells when smallmouth fishing. So he soaks his baits in Nories scent juice in Tupperware containers. This allows the baits to soak in the smell and attract smallmouth to bite better. 
#Bassmaster #BassFishing #BASSElite
